<H4>    Spokesman Views Resignation </H4>

<F P=102> OW0804120494 Beijing XINHUA in English 1140 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0804120494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
