  [Text] Beijing, April 11 (XINHUA) -- There are now more 
than 5,000 overseas agencies in Beijing, posing pressure on the 
supply of office space. 
  Local officials said that the number of business agencies of 
internationally-known companies keeps rising in the Chinese 
